{
  "texts": [
    "The primary context of these documents may be something other than medical.",
    "The words 'claim' and 'said' appear in 9 out of 10 of the clusters.",
    "This is expected due to the language used in the original articles, and the labels may need to convey clearly what the cluster is about.The last piece of the pipeline extracts the named entities.",
    "This would help us get to know and understand the cluster better.",
    "In Table 4, we can see the 5 most frequently generated entities for each cluster.By examining the top 5 entities in cluster 6, particularly CDC (Centers for Disease Control and Prevention), Medicare, and WHO (World Health Organization), it is evident that the primary theme of this cluster is related to medical topics."
  ]
}